			<h3>Finding what you want in WHUFU</h3>
			<ul id="findlist">
				<li><a href="?page=search&type=home">Spot Search</a> &ndash; Our crack Marketing Research team has determined that most casual browsers just want to find cool places - places to camp, hot springs, that sort of thing. For that we have a <a href="?page=search&type=home">boatload of ways</a> to search through the hundreds of spots.</li>
