				<li>Text Search &ndash; The "search text" box above will look for text in all stories, picture labels, maps and trip logs. Friends can type their names in there to see if I said anything mean about them. Enter the name of a town or a beach, or <em>hot springs</em> or <em>fishing</em> or whatever strikes your fancy.</li>
			</ul>
			<p>Whatever method you use, you will soon end up at something interesting. The whole point of WHUFU is that it is <em>rich in interconnections</em>. Related pictures, stories, maps shound be a click away no matter where you are. My hope is that you will be intrigued to follow those links for a while.</p>
